{"tid":1406922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拆彈專家入來］","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:25:43.000Z","uid":296285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02eb921bba2da9b5ca904733167ba693ffb92bfe","tid":1406922,"uid":296285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"唉。其實有無人覺得是一個惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n政府不回應市民。<br />\n示威者要加大力度去示威。<br />\n令警察要加大力度 去制服 加大力度的示威者。<br />\n然後警民衝突惡化。<br />\n<br />\n然後政府又堅持不回應。<br />\n示威者又再再加大力度。<br />\nRepeat all again...<br />\n<br />\n講真土生土長的我，真的不忍心個局面越來越惡化。<br />\n因為我真的很喜歡香港呢個地方。<br />\n到底要有多黑心的政府才可以忍心這樣繼惡化落去。<br />\n好似係鬥緊邊一方讓步先。<br />\n<br />\n唉，真係唔知可以點收科。<br />\n無敵連登仔，有無咩方法可以拆得店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}